data.name: Rcon Plus
data.summary: Adds A Bunch Of New Rcon Commands For Server Owners To Use.
data.description:
You Can Add This Mod To Your Server By Using The Command UGCAddMod UGC3462586

If You Have Ideas For More Custom Commands, You Can Message Me On Discord: KodaTheProto

Argument Usage:
{Player} = All, {Team}, TTTRole, UniqueID
{Boolean} = True, False, 1, 0
{Object} = All, Bodies, Items, Vehicles
{Team} = RedTeam, BlueTeam, 0, 1

Commands:
- Notify {Player} {Message Here} | display text in front of the player to communicate to them through RCON
- DropItems {Player} | forces the player to drop all the items they are holding
- DisablePickup {Player} {Boolean} | prevents the target player from picking up any items
- DisableMovement {Player} {Boolean} | disables movement for the target player
- CleanUp {Object} | destroys all idle objects you specify
- Godmode {Player} {Boolean} | makes the target player immune to all damage
- Warp {Player} {UniqueID} | teleports target player to the player with matching uniqueid
- AddBot {Amount} {Team} | adds the amount of bots you specify to the selected team
- RemoveBot {Amount} {Team} | removes the amount of bots you specify from the select team (removing 0 bots will remove all bots on that team)
- Ignite {Player} | sets the target player on fire
- DisableItems {Player} {Boolean} | disables the target player from using items (ie, firing a gun)
- Detonate {Player} | makes the target player spontaneously explode
- GameSpeed {Multiplier} | changes the speed of the game to the multiplier you set (1 is default)
- SetGravity {Multiplier} | changes the gravity for all objects to the multiplier you set (1 in default)
- EnableProne {Boolean} | allows players to enter prone in any game mode
- FallDamage {Boolean} | sets weather players can be damaged from falling
- EnableBuyMenu {Player} {Boolean} | enables the buy menu for the target player
- NoClip {Player} {Boolean} | allows the target player to fly and move through objects freely
- Supply {Player} {ItemID} | gives the target player an infinite amount of the item you specify
- Visibility {Player} {Boolean} | sets the target player's visibility to other players (does not hide ttt nametags)
